{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e402d8ea56","title":"对浙江执行侨务政策情况报道的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a2beab7321","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":8,"articleId":"e402d8ea56"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"968330044c","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗瑞卿，当时任公安部部长。"},{"id":"913725f2d4","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新华社《内部参考》1956年12月6日第二〇七一期刊登的《浙江省许多地区在执行侨务政策中存在不少严重缺点》。文内说，出席浙江省最近召开的侨卷、归侨代表会议的代表反映，浙江各地（特别是农村）在对待侨着和归侨方面存在许多问题。不少青年由于亲属在国外不能入团，甚至入工会也受阻碍；国外来信被拆阅以至传阅；干涉侨汇使用，强迫借贷、捐款和购买公债；一些公安部门对归国观光、探亲的华侨出国多方限制、留难。代表们认为，政府的政策是很好的，但宣传工作做得不够，下面执行得不好，要求大力开展对侨务政策的宣传，重视贯彻侨务政策的问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c3805c3f90","type":"title","text":"对浙江执行侨务政策情况报道的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56"},{"id":"968330044c","type":"paragraph","text":"罗瑞卿同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56"},{"id":"913725f2d4","type":"paragraph","text":"111页上关于浙江省的一条消息值得一看。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56"},{"id":"b2e159241c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56"},{"id":"9ac5f5808b","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56"}],"page":{"id":"99f5eb0181","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e402d8ea56","start":184,"end":184}}}},"__N_SSG":true}